<bibRefCitation id="336E4B25FFE7416AC8D2EED4FC9F27B7" author="Glenn, G. S. Jr." box="[660,813,1976,2002]" pageId="17" pageNumber="468" pagination="67 - 102" refId="ref16270" refString="Glenn, G. S. Jr. (1991) A systematic revision of Enyaliopsis Karsch 1887 (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae, Hetrodinae). Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 117, 67 - 102. http: // www. jstor. org / stable / 25078540" type="journal article" year="1991">Glenn (1991)</bibRefCitation>
